description: Bird B Gone Pond Defenders are UV protected interlocking polypropylene plastic disks that float just below the surface of your pond or water garden, creating a shelter for pond fish like KOI against predators. The Pond Defender Set consists of 12 disks that interlock together in seconds to fit the shape of any pond. Pond Defender disks are less intrusive than traditional pond surface netting and the various openings within each disk allow for continuous plant growth. Virtually invisible once installed, Bird B Gone Pond Defenders will not ruin the aesthetic design of your pond or water garden. Bird B Gone Pond Defender disks are easy to interlock using the supplied clips and the system can be easily removed for cleaning and pond maintenance. 12 per pack.
